metadata.name: The Psychonaut's Tarot #1 : The Magician
metadata.description:
The Magician represents the willpower and skill necessary to complete a task or otherwise manifest a desired outcome. The fire points to the heavens, while the cannabis plants represent the Earth and nature. The four suits of the Tarot - the cup, club, wand, and sword - are manifested from the magical smoke. The infinity symbol represents the infinite capabilities of the human mind.

Approximately 70 mm by 120 mm (2.75" x 4.75"), 825 px by 1425 px, 300 dpi.
